79,000円キャッシュバック</a><img src=\"//ad.jp.ap.valuecommerce.com/servlet/gifbanner?sid=3774937&pid=892653516\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\"></li>\n    <li><a href=\"//ck.jp.ap.valuecommerce.com/servlet/referral?sid=3774937&pid=892653518\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#ea580c;color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;\">▶ auひかり｜auスマホユーザーならさらにおトク！</a><img src=\"//ad.jp.ap.valuecommerce.com/servlet/gifbanner?sid=3774937&pid=892653518\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\"></li>\n  </ul>\n</div>"
